snippet.title: Project X Zone 2 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the Launch Trailer for Project X Zone 2, the ultimate RPG mashup featuring legendary characters from Sega, Capcom and Bandai Namco! Project X Zone 2 is releases in North America on February 16th exclusively on Nintendo 3DS!

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com
